OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1771963514
OL,3,CCCTV images released after bacon put
OL,4,Con door of mosque during Ramadan
OL,5,Cprayers
OL,7,FPolice have released CCTV images of a
OL,8,Fman in connection with an
OL,9,Finvestigation into a hate crime after
OL,10,Fbacon was put on a glass door of a
OL,11,Fmosque during prayer.
OL,13,FThe incident happened at a mosque on
OL,14,FCheltenham Road during the first week
OL,15,Fof Ramadan and was reported in the
OL,16,Fafternoon of Friday 20 February.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
