OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1771963514
OL,3,CCCTV images released after bacon put
OL,4,Con door of mosque during Ramadan
OL,5,Cprayers
OL,7,FOfficers say CCTV enquiries and
OL,8,Fstatements have been taken, increased
OL,9,Fpatrols have been carried out to
OL,10,Fprovide a visible reassurance, and
OL,11,Fthey are in contact with the victims
OL,12,Fand other mosques while enquiries
OL,13,Fcontinue.
OL,15,FAvon and Somerset Police have now
OL,16,Freleased CCTV images of a man they
OL,17,Fwant to speak to in connection with
OL,18,Fthe investigation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1771963514
OL,3,CCCTV images released after bacon put
OL,4,Con door of mosque during Ramadan
OL,5,Cprayers
OL,7,FThe man in the image has been
OL,8,Fdescribed as a male, with a bald head
OL,9,Fwho was wearing a high-visibility
OL,10,Ftrousers and a dark jacket.
OL,12,FNeighbourhoods' Chief Inspector Serena
OL,13,FSerjeant said: "This was a deliberate
OL,14,Fact which has caused significant
OL,15,Fconcern to the community during a
OL,16,Fperiod of heightened religious
OL,17,Fobservance, and we will not tolerate
OL,18,Fhate in our communities.
OL,26,@uD@POU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1771963514
OL,3,CCCTV images released after bacon put
OL,4,Con door of mosque during Ramadan
OL,5,Cprayers
OL,7,F"We promptly attended the scene upon
OL,8,Freceiving the report and we are
OL,9,Fcontinuing to engage with mosque
OL,10,Fleaders throughout Ramadan following
OL,11,Fthis appalling incident, and we will
OL,12,Fcontinue to offer our support and
OL,13,Fassurance.
OL,15,F"We are treating this as a religiously
OL,16,Faggravated public order offence, and
OL,17,Fwe would urge anybody with information
OL,18,Fon the incident or the identity of the
OL,19,Findividual concerned to contact us."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
